IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB & HARYANA AT CHANDIGARH CWP No. 8170 of 1994 Date of Decision:08.11.2012 Dinesh Chander & others ..............PETITIONERS

vs. Haryana State Electricity Board and others ...........RESPONDENTS CORAM:- HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE G.S. SANDHAWALIA Present:- Mr.O.P.Goyal, Sr.Advocate, with Ms.Amanpreet Kaur, Advocate, for the petitioners, None for the respondents.
